celona Airport. See our How to Arrive page for more details on how to get to Tossa de Mar.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>SurroundingArea</Type><Text>The hotel is situated on the more private Mar Menuda beach, separated from the main beach by a rocky outcrop, and a wonderful place for both adults and kids  to sunbathe, swim, go snorkelling or even scuba diving.</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>PropertyInformation</Type><Text>Spacious restaurant to enjoy the famous Mediterranean cuisine, replete with fresh local produce, and showcasing excellent seafood and meat dishes.  Buffet breakfast is offered, as well as cooking shows.  Meanwhile, the bar staff will be happy to mix your favourite cocktail, be it a Caipirinha, Mojito or simple Gin and Tonic, and provide a selection of appetisers and other snacks</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>DiningFacilities</Type><Text>Spacious restaurant to enjoy the famous Mediterranean cuisine, replete with fresh local produce, and showcasing excellent seafood and meat dishes.  Buffet breakfast is offered, as well as cooking shows.  Meanwhile, the bar staff will be happy to mix your favourite cocktail, be it a Caipirinha, Mojito or simple Gin and Tonic, and provide a selection of appetisers and other snacks</Text></Description><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>Short</Type><Text>Medium Size Lobby</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Sauna</Code><Text>Sauna</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Whirlpool</Code><Text>Whirlpool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>IndoorPool</Code><Text>Indoor swimming pool</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>AirConditioning</Code><Text>Air conditioning</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>RoomService</Code><Text>Room service</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Hair dryer</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>Mon